.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 772px) 100vw, 772px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you are looking for a free just page caching plugin than look no further than <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-super-cache/\">WP Super Cache</a>. It has a lot fewer features than WP-Rocket but gets the job done.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-super-cache/\"><strong>WP Super Cache</strong></a> <span class=\"label label-success\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-super-cache/\">Free Version</a></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-super-cache/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3745 size-full\" src=\"https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/banner-772x250.png\" alt=\"Best Caching Plugin\" width=\"772\" height=\"264\" srcset=\"https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/banner-772x250.png 772w, https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/banner-772x250-400x137.png 400w, https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/banner-772x250-768x263.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 772px) 100vw, 772px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Some people might say, what about <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/w3-total-cache/\">W3 Total Cache</a>. Well since this is my honest opinion I have had tons of issues with this plugin mostly due to the complexity and end users not knowing how to use it. If you are super technically maybe you&#8217;d enjoy it.</p>\n<p><a href=\"#plugin-categories\">↑ Back to Plugin Categories</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"#forms-plugins\">Best Forms (Contact Form) Plugins</h2>\n<p>OK, this one is hard. I&#8217;m going to list 4 plugins and it&#8217;s really hard to go wrong with any of these. They all will get the job done when it comes to creating simple contact forms to complex forms. I personally use <a href=\"https://www.gravityforms.com/\">Gravity Forms</a> because I have been using a WordPress a long time and they were the only ones that existed when I got into the market.</p>\n<p>So first up <a href=\"https://www.gravityforms.com/\">Gravity Form</a>. Gravity Forms is the oldest among the form plugins listed. But it&#8217;s still a tried and true solution. It has never failed me.</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://www.gravityforms.com/\">Gravity Forms</a></strong> <span class=\"label label-primary\"><a href=\"https://www.gravityforms.com/\">Pro Version</a></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gravityforms.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3748 size-full\" src=\"https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/gravity-forms.jpg\" alt=\"Best Forms Plugin\" width=\"772\" height=\"183\" srcset=\"https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/gravity-forms.jpg 772w, https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/gravity-forms-400x95.jpg 400w, https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/gravity-forms-768x182.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 772px) 100vw, 772px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Next, we have <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\">WPForms</a>. It&#8217;s the new kid on the block but it was created by <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/about-us/\">Jared Atchison, Syed Balkhi and Thomas Griffin</a>. I know these guys personally and I can say that anything they make is going to be awesome.</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\">WPForms</a></strong> <span class=\"label label-success\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wpforms-lite/\">Free Version</a></span> <span class=\"label label-primary\"><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\">Pro Version</a></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3749 size-full\" src=\"https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/wpforms.jpg\" alt=\"Best Forms Plugin\" width=\"772\" height=\"239\" srcset=\"https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/wpforms.jpg 772w, https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/wpforms-400x124.jpg 400w, https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/wpforms-768x238.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 772px) 100vw, 772px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Looking for a great free Forms plugin? Than <a href=\"https://ninjaforms.com/\">Ninja Forms</a> by <a href=\"http://jameslaws.com/\">James Laws</a> and team is an excellent choice. They have a unique form builder experience and provide add-ons for advanced functionality.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ninjaforms.com/\"><strong>Ninja Forms</strong></a> <span class=\"label label-success\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/ninja-forms/\">Free Version</a></span> <span class=\"label label-primary\"><a href=\"https://ninjaforms.com/pricing/\">Pro Version</a></span><strong><a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/ninja-forms.jpg\"><br />\n</a><a href=\"https://ninjaforms.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3750 size-full\" src=\"https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/ninja-forms.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"772\" height=\"258\" srcset=\"https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/ninja-forms.jpg 772w, https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/ninja-forms-400x134.jpg 400w, https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/ninja-forms-768x257.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 772px) 100vw, 772px\" /></a></strong></p>\n<p>While I have personally never used this forms plugin I know many people including many of my customers who do and  I have only heard good things about it. Plus the owners behind the company, <a href=\"http://strategy11.com/about/\">Steve and Stephanie</a>, are great people.</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://formidableforms.com/\">Formidable</a></strong> <span class=\"label label-success\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/formidable/\">Free Version</a></span> <span class=\"label label-primary\"><a href=\"https://formidableforms.com/\">Pro Version</a></span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://formidableforms.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3756 size-full\" src=\"https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/formidable.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"772\" height=\"213\" srcset=\"https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/formidable.jpg 772w, https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/formidable-400x110.jpg 400w, https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/formidable-768x212.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 772px) 100vw, 772px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"#plugin-categories\">↑ Back to Plugin Categories</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"#calendar-plugin\">Best Calendar Plugins</h2>\n<p>When it comes to a calendar plugin I generally just <a href=\"http://www.wpbeginner.com/plugins/how-to-add-google-calendar-in-wordpress/\">embed a Google Calendar</a> in the WordPress page or post. But sometimes Google Calendar is not the best solution and you need a native calendar solution for WordPress. For example, a university I worked at needed an Academic Calendar. The best plugin to do the job with free and pro version is&#8230;</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/the-events-calendar/\">The Events Calendar</a></strong> <span class=\"label label-success\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/the-events-calendar/\">Free Version</a></span> <span class=\"label label-primary\"><a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/product/wordpress-events-calendar-pro/\">Pro Version</a></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/the-events-calendar/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3757 size-full\" src=\"https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/banner-772x250-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"772\" height=\"250\" srcset=\"https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/banner-772x250-1.png 772w, https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/banner-772x250-1-400x130.png 400w, https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/banner-772x250-1-768x249.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 772px) 100vw, 772px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"#plugin-categories\">↑ Back to Plugin Categories</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"social-sharing-plugin\">Best Social Sharing Plugins</h2>\n<p>So everyone wants to add social sharing buttons to their blog post right? Well most people do, if you are one of those people then check out these two plugins.</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/jetpack/\">Social Sharing in JetPack</a> (<a href=\"https://jetpack.com/support/sharing/\">how to</a>)</strong> <span class=\"label label-success\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/jetpack/\">Free Version</a></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/jetpack/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3761 size-full\" src=\"https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/banner-772x250-2.png\" alt=\"Best Social Sharing\" width=\"772\" height=\"250\" srcset=\"https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/banner-772x250-2.png 772w, https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/banner-772x250-2-400x130.png 400w, https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/banner-772x250-2-768x249.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 772px) 100vw, 772px\" /></a></p>\n<p>While not specifically a WordPress plugin, the social sharing app from <a href=\"https://sumo.com/\">Sumo.com</a> is great.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sumo.com/app/share\"><strong>Sumo Sharing</strong></a> <span class=\"label label-primary\"><a href=\"https://sumo.com/app/share\">Pro Version</a></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/sumo.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3762\" src=\"https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/sumo.jpg\" alt=\"Best Social Sharing Plugin\" width=\"772\" height=\"409\" srcset=\"https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/sumo.jpg 772w, https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/sumo-400x212.jpg 400w, https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/sumo-768x407.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 772px) 100vw, 772px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"#plugin-categories\">↑ Back to Plugin Categories</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"best-site-migration-plugin\">Best Site Migration Plugins</h2>\n<p>Ever wanted to build your WordPress site in your local development environment or on a staging server then migrate it to a live WordPress site. Then you need a site migration plugin and the best one without a doubt is <a href=\"https://deliciousbrains.com/wp-migrate-db-pro/\">WP DB Migrate</a> by Brad Tournard and the <a href=\"https://deliciousbrains.com/\">Delicious Brains</a> team.</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://deliciousbrains.com/wp-migrate-db-pro/\">WP DB Migrate</a></strong> <span class=\"label label-success\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-migrate-db/\">Free Version</a></span> <span class=\"label label-primary\"><a href=\"https://deliciousbrains.com/wp-migrate-db-pro/\">Pro Version</a></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://deliciousbrains.com/wp-migrate-db-pro/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3763 size-full\" src=\"https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/banner-772x250.jpg\" alt=\"Best Site Migration Plugin\" width=\"772\" height=\"250\" srcset=\"https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/banner-772x250.jpg 772w, https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/banner-772x250-400x130.jpg 400w, https://www.seedprod.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/banner-772x250-768x249.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 772px) 100vw, 772px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"#plugin-categories\">↑ Back to Plugin Categories</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"security-plugins\">Best Security Plugins</h2>\n<p>Security is a very important aspect to any WordPress site. Since WordPress is so popular it&#8217;s a very big target. So with that said you&#8217;d better have some way to protect your WordPress website. While some host have some sort of security layer you&#8217;ll probably want to take some extra steps to harden your website.</p>\n<p>I personally use <a href=\"https://www.cloudflare.com/\">CloudFlare Pro</a> which protects my site from brute force attacks, DDoS attacks, and they have a Web Application Firewall to protect from other attacks.  I pay $20 a month for this.</p>\n<p>But these plugins are great alternatives and all achieve the same thing, hardening WordPress.</p>\n<p><strong><a href